results.description:
An All-New, All-Different Marvel series. After his adventures in the Secret Wars Old Man Logan Vol.1 mini-series, the older Logan is transported to the Main Marvel Universe. The series lasted for 50 issues, and was continued in the concluding Dead Man Logan 12 part mini-series.

Collected Editions

  • Wolverine: Old Man Logan: Berzerker (#1-4)
  • Wolverine: Old Man Logan: Bordertown (#5-8)
  • Wolverine: Old Man Logan: The Last Ronin (#9-13)
  • Wolverine: Old Man Logan: Old Monsters (#14-18)
  • Wolverine: Old Man Logan: Past Lives (#19-24)
  • Wolverine: Old Man Logan: Days of Anger (#25-30)
  • Wolverine: Old Man Logan: Days of Anger Black and White Edition (#25-30)
  • Wolverine: Old Man Logan: Scarlet Samurai (#31-35)
  • Wolverine: Old Man Logan: To Kill For (#36-40)
  • Wolverine: Old Man Logan: The Hunter and the Hunted (#41-45)
  • Wolverine: Old Man Logan: End of the World (#46-50 & Annual #1)
